      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card claims a function 'exportPeakMatrixForSTREAM' which does not appear in the paper.",
        "STREAM is not mentioned as a tool integrated with ArchR. The paper explicitly implements trajectory analysis with Slingshot and Monocle 3, not STREAM.",
        "The research question assumes ArchR has STREAM-specific export functionality, but the paper provides no evidence of this.",
