      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms ArchR performs multiome integration but does not explicitly name the specific R functions (importFeatureMatrix, addGeneExpressionMatrix, addIterativeLSI, addCombinedDims). The paper describes the workflow conceptually but function names are not mentioned in the provided passages. These are likely correct based on ArchR documentation, but cannot be verified from the paper text alone.",
