      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms ArchR provides multi-omic integration and dimensionality reduction (iterative LSI mentioned in passage 8). However, the specific function names (importFeatureMatrix, addGeneExpressionMatrix, addIterativeLSI, addCombinedDims) are not mentioned in the passages. The paper does not list these specific function names.",
