      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "ArchR provides a user-focused interface for complex scATAC-seq analysis, such as marker feature identification, transcription factor (TF) footprinting, interactive sequencing track visualization, scRNA-seq integration and cellular trajectory identification",
      "asbval:note": "ArchR is confirmed as the primary tool. While specific function names (addIterativeLSI, addCombinedDims) are not mentioned in passages, iterative LSI and multiome integration are explicitly described as ArchR capabilities.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41588-021-00790-6",
