      "asbval:evidence_quote": "ArchR facilitates cellular trajectory analysis to identify the predicted path of gene regulatory changes from one set of cells to another... In addition to implementing both Slingshot and Monocle 3, two scRNA-seq trajectory algorithms, ArchR also provides its own supervised trajectory analysis.",
