    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/single-cell-chromatin-data-handling/004",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "ArchR facilitates cellular trajectory analysis to identify the predicted path of gene regulatory changes from one set of cells to another, a unique type of insight enabled by single-cell data. In addition to implementing both Slingshot and Monocle 3 (refs. 40\u201343), two scRNA-seq trajectory algorithms, ArchR also provides its own supervised trajectory analysis.",
      "asbval:note": "ArchR does support trajectory analysis after peak calling and cell annotation, but integrates Slingshot and Monocle 3 natively rather than exporting matrices to external tools. No evidence of STREAM integration or matrix export functionality.",
